# Trailing slashes
/recipes /recipes/ 301
/about /about/ 301
/contact /contact/ 301
/privacy /privacy/ 301

# Legacy/alternate URLs
/categories /recipes/ 301
/categories/* /recipes/ 301
/recipe/* /recipes/:splat 301

# Social shortcuts
/pinterest https://pinterest.com/homerecipeblog 302
/instagram https://instagram.com/homerecipeblog 302
/facebook https://facebook.com/homerecipeblog 302

# Common misspellings
/recipies/* /recipes/:splat 301
/receipes/* /recipes/:splat 301
